Safety during the server W-DECODE legs: AC power; `pmset -g therm` reported no
thermal or performance warning.  Swap used was 1,429 MB before server work and
1,373 MB after it.  Pageouts rose from 448958 to 449707 pages (about 11.7 MB
at the 16 KB page size), below the 100 MB bound.  This is still a
**non-baseline** result because the machine was not otherwise idle and
`powermetrics`/J-token data is unavailable.
